          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;State Strategic Stockpile Act of 2023&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This bill reauthorizes through FY2028 grants that support states with establishing, expanding, and maintaining stockpiles of medical supplies for use during declared disasters or emergencies.&amp;nbsp; &lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
